  <h3 id='veterinary_app_key_features'>Key features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Dashboard:</span> key system statistics (clients, pets, consultations, appointments, etc.) with dynamic graphs.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Role and permission system:</span> detailed access control for different types of users.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">User management:</span> system account administration.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Positions:</span> definition of internal roles such as veterinarians, assistants, administrators, etc.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Veterinarians:</span> registration and control of medical staff.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Species:</span> classification of pets by species (dogs, cats, rabbits, etc.).
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Vaccines:</span> registration and administration of vaccines available for pets, including general information and individual follow-up.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Clients:</span> administration of pet owners.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Pets:</span> medical and general information for each pet.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Veterinary consultations:</span> medical history, symptoms, diagnoses, and treatments.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Events and calendar:</span> scheduled veterinary appointments with a calendar view.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Complete inventory:</span> product categories, warehouses, stock and movements, suppliers.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Sales:</span> registration and management of invoices for each product sold to a customer.
    </li>
  </ul>
